Class SKZoomLevelConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  com.skobbler.ngx.navigation.SKZoomLevelConfiguration

public class SKZoomLevelConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object

SKZoomLevelConfiguration stores information about the speed interval for a zoom level that will be used during navigation.

Version:
3.0

SKZoomLevelConfiguration

public SKZoomLevelConfiguration(float minSpeed,
                                float maxSpeed,
                                float zoomLevel)
Parameters:
minSpeed - The minimumSpeed provided in km/h for a specified zoom level.
maxSpeed - The maximumSpeed provided in km/h for a specified zoom level.
zoomLevel - The zoom level for the defined speed interval. The value of this property must be between 0.0 and 19.0.
